salt 為proxy server 
scripts 放置/etc/salt/deploy/scripts

====slat 指令   salt hostname cmd.run "cat /hmoe/xxx.conf"
015*fe* 
015*be*
015*pay*
015*app*

salt 015*app* test.ping  <測試ping015app>
salt 015*app* cmd.run "cat /vhost/*.conf | grep  123.937.639.167"


====slat 使用scripts 方法
salt "041*pay*01*" cmd.script salt://scripts/domain-check.sh
